@startuml
actor Dispatcher
participant Frontend
participant Backend
participant "TMS Bridge" as TMSBridge
database "TMS Database" as TMS
participant "TMS Pulse" as TMSPulse
participant OMS

title "Pickup Planning - New Dispo Leg Creation Flow"

== Flow 2: Transport Planning Process ==

Dispatcher -> Frontend : Drag Leg onto planning area
Frontend -> Backend : Request to add Leg to Transport Order

activate Backend
Backend -> TMSBridge : Add Leg to Transport Order
TMSBridge -> TMS : Execute pDis_TransportOrder.AddLeg()

activate TMS
TMS -> TMS : Create new TMS-Leg
TMS -> TMS : Execute internal business logic\nfor adding legs
note right of TMS
No conflict regarding Data Integrity
as the Leg data is TMS-internal anyway.

For New Dispo it doesn't matter if the
Legs are already present or created instantly
in that moment on behalf of New Dispo.
end note
TMS --> TMSBridge : Leg added successfully\n and Leg-ID returned
deactivate TMS

TMSBridge --> Backend : Return Leg-ID
Backend -> Backend : Store Leg-Id reference\nin existing New Dispo Leg
Backend --> Frontend : Return success
deactivate Backend

Frontend -> Dispatcher : Show updated planning view

' == Flow 3: TMS-Leg Creation in UniFace ==

' Dispatcher -> UniFace : Create TMS-Leg
' UniFace -> TMS : Request to create Leg\nand run business logic

' activate TMS
' TMS -> TMS : Create Leg
' TMS -> TMS : Execute business logic
' TMS -> TMS : Set Leg status to "planned"
' TMS -> TMS : Update table "sendung"
' TMS --> UniFace : Leg created successfully
' deactivate TMS

' TMSPulse -> TMS : Detect change on table "sendung"
' TMS --> TMSPulse : Record change detected
' TMSPulse -> Backend : Send data change event

' activate Backend
' Backend -> Backend : Apply Leg-detection filters
' Backend -> Backend : Check if change is Leg-related
' alt Leg detected
'     Backend -> Backend : Extract Leg information\nincluding SEN_TIX value
'     Backend -> Backend : Search leg database\nfor matching SEN_TIX id
'     Backend -> Backend : Set leg status to "planned"
'     Backend -> Frontend : Propagate status change
'     Frontend -> Dispatcher : Display updated Leg status
' end
' deactivate Backend

@enduml